name: Fans Halter-neck Tankini
description:
A flattering and feminine tank top with halter neckline, darts in bust and finished with double ties and gathered side seams. This can definitely be worn out of the water!

FANS PRINT: Set on a background of mother of pearl and gold leaf, this design has the softest pallet of colours in the collection. I wanted to bring dragonfly’s and fans into the range and in this design we managed to bring both of these quintessentially Japanese images into one design. This piece of artwork is delicate both in its gentle illustration and gorgeous pastel colours. I added beautiful Persian Crimson ties here to bring out the highlights in the fans in the image. A really feminine top, this print looks particularly good on girls with lovely pale delicate skin type.

Other pieces in the collection that match beautifully with this top are the cheeky pants with gathered sides either in the Fans Print or the Silvery Blue. 

***The Halter neck tankini comes in sizes 8 thru to 16 for all shapes and sizes...please just indicate on the purchase page the size you require. This garment is also available in 3 of my other designs where available. See my store.

name: String Bikini
description:
STRING BIKINI - Sliding halter style top with ties and Brazilian style minimal briefs with tie sides.

SONG BIRDS: This image is one my close girlfriend and I spent hours and hours perfecting…We wanted to bring this lovely bird that Rob had painstakingly drawn for us into the collection and we felt the range needed a gorgeous blue to work in with the rest of the colours we had already chosen. We combined a selection of our favourite images in the range and brought them together finally settling on this lovely rich teal background. Then our song bird really took flight. We hope you love this one us much as we do….

****The String bikini comes in sizes 8 thru to 14 (see size chart below)...please just indicate on the purchase page the size you require. This style also comes in all of my other 4 designs. See my store.

name: Rashi cover-up Surf shirt in Chocolate with Song Birds Print
description:
Rashi surf shirt with cap raglan sleeve. This is great for girls who like to surf or who just like a bit more protection from the sun. This shirt comes in a lovely deep ash chocolate colour with the Song Birds featured in the sleeves and neckband. I also do this shirt in the Red Pohutakawa print.

This shirt is a great extra over your swimsuit or is a good match with either a bikini pant or some sexy hotpants from my range. It comes in sizes 8 through to 16 for all shapes and sizes. (see size chart below). Please just indicate which size you prefer on the final sale page.

name: Tri Bikini in Maple Leaf
description:
TRI BIKINI – Sliding Tri top with ties and a low cut easy fit pant.

MAPLE LEAVES: This was the first image in the collection. The maple leaf is just such a stunning image, invoking wonderful autumn colours and memories. My love for Japanese art and textiles is really epitomised in the image of the maple leaf and I couldn’t go past it when I fist was looking for inspiration for my collection. The black background is of course timeless, classic and suits so many skin types and body shapes. A sexy and minimal design, this bikini is hot, hot, hot!

The Tri slide bikini comes in sizes 8 thru to 14 (see size chart below)...please just indicate on the purchase page the size you require. It is also available in all of my other prints, just check my shop.

name: Plunging One Piece swimsuit
description:
This is a classic timeless one-piece swimsuit. Simple and elegant it has low cut legs and a plunging neckline giving it a sexy yet classic look. I have put double ties at the neckline with a halter feel. I kept the layout pretty minimal here with another lily coming down over the mid back...

THE LILY PRINT : This image is of a Tiger lily delicately hand drawn and digitally sculpted in various hews through charcoal to silver… highlights are in the rich Golds and sunburnt Oranges of the Tiger lily. This image is timeless and super feminine with a clean white background, one of my personal favourites in the collection. The ties at the neckline of this swimsuit are in a gorgeous gold that brings out the colours at the centre of the flower.

This swimsuit also comes in 3 other prints..see my store..

The One piece swimsuit comes in sizes 8 thru to 16 for all shapes and sizes...please just indicate on the purchase page the size you require.
